ory]] || ''[[Finding Nemo (franchise)|Finding Nemo]]'' || {{n}} || {{n}} || {{y}}{{ref|Con|Con}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Drax the Destroyer]] || ''[[Guardians of the Galaxy (film)|Guardians of the Galaxy]]'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Elsa (Frozen)|Elsa]] || ''Frozen'' || {{y}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Star Wars Rebels#Crew of the Ghost|Ezra Bridger]] || ''[[Star Wars Rebels]]'' || {{n}} || {{n}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Falcon (comics)|Falcon]] || ''The Avengers'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Fear]] || ''Inside Out'' || {{n}} || {{n}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Finn (Star Wars)|Finn]] || ''[[Star Wars: The Force Awakens]]'' || {{n}} || {{n}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[List of Cars characters#World Grand Prix Racers|Francesco Bernoulli]] || ''[[Cars (franchise)|Cars]]'' || {{y}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Gamora]] || ''Guardians of the Galaxy'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Norman Osborn|Green Goblin]] || ''Ultimate Spider-Man'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Groot]] || ''Guardians of the Galaxy'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Han Solo]] || ''Star Wars'' || {{n}} || {{n}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Hawkeye (Clint Barton)|Hawkeye]] || ''The Avengers'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Hiro Takachiho|Hiro Hamada]] || ''Big Hero 6'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[List of Cars characters#Holley Shiftwell|Holley Shiftwell]] || ''Cars'' || {{y}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[Hulk]] || ''The Avengers'' || {{n}} || {{y}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| Hulkbuster Iron Man || ''[[Avengers: Age of Ultron]]'' || {{n}} || {{n}} || {{y}}\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:l